info.description: Find the hidden word by describing it without using forbidden phrases. Take turns giving clues while teammates guess within a time limit. Gain points for each correct guess, and the team with the highest score wins.

info.ruleText:
1. Teams & Players 🧑‍🤝‍🧑

    • Divide into two teams by clicking on the seats.
    • Each team takes turns having one 'clue-giver' and the rest as guessers.

  2. Game Setup 🎲

    • Make sure to use voice chat software. This game is about talking.
    • Press restart_alt to select your language and start a new game.

  3. Playing a Turn 🕐

    • The clue-giver (highlighted seat) presses play_arrow to draw the first card and tries to get their team to guess the word at the top of the card.
    • The catch? They can't use the forbidden words listed below it.
    • The clue-giver can give any verbal clues but cannot say part of the sought-after word, spell it out, or say rhymes-with or sounds-like phrases.
    • When the team mates guess the correct word, the clue-giver uses done to move the card to the done pile.

  4. Forbidden Words 🚫

    • If the clue-giver uses a forbidden word, an opponent should point it out by making an obnoxious noise.
    • Either the clue-giver or an opponent clicks close to move the card to the appropriate pile.

  5. Time Limit ⏳

    • Each turn lasts for one minute.
    • When time's up, use skip_next to pass play to the next team.

  6. Scoring Points 🎯

    • One point is scored for each card correctly guessed.
    • Points are also scored if the opposing team's clue-giver uses a forbidden word.

  7. Winning the Game 🏆

    • After a set number of rounds or when all cards are used, the team with the most points wins.
